een TV, free Wi-Fi and luxury bathroom amenities from the Appelles Black range. Access to our Signature Lounge is daily from 6:00am including buffet breakfast, drinks throughout the day and evening canapes served with Happy Hour cocktails.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-47h9qicr fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47h9qidf fg-row row     fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47h9qidp fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h2 class=\"ffb-id-47h9qidr fg-heading text-left    fg-text-dark\">AMENITITES<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-648mklpp fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 room-amenities fg-text-dark\"><p class=\"ffb-id-648mklpq fg-paragraph text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- Access to our Signature Lounge<\/p>\n<p>- Air conditioning<\/p>\n<p>- Hair Dryer<\/p>\n<p>- Spa (Chargeable)<\/p>\n<p><\/p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-648ms22d fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-648ms22e fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>- Nespresso coffee machine<\/p>\n<p>- Mini Bar (Chargeable)<\/p>\n<p>- Non-smoking Room<\/p>\n<p>- Safety Deposit Box<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4ov68ai7 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/be.synxis.com\/?Hotel=3592&#038;room=EXC\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-xs    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">BOOK NOW<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47h9qi7u{ padding-top: 30px;padding-bottom: 30px;}.ffb-id-47h9qi82{ padding-top: 30px;padding-right: 30px;padding-bottom: 30px;padding-left: 30px;}.ffb-id-4ov68ai7 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ color:#ffffff;}.ffb-id-4ov68ai7 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ color:#ffffff;}.ffb-id-4ov68ai7 .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ border-color: transparent;}.ffb-id-4ov